sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Entry as testcase_wash.py
    participant Builder as PipelineBuilder
    participant Pipeline as Pipeline
    participant Reader as TestCaseJsonReader
    participant ClassParse as TestCaseClassParseStage
    participant CorpusParse as TestCaseCorpusParseStage
    participant Enrich as TestCaseEnrichStage
    participant Writer as TestCaseFileWriter

    User->>Entry: --input ./input --output ./output
    Entry->>Builder: build_test_case_pipeline(config)
    Builder-->>Pipeline: 构建完成的管道
    Entry->>Pipeline: run(config)

    Pipeline->>Reader: process(config)
    Note right of Reader: 扫描文件夹中所有 JSON, 仅提取 metadata
    Reader-->>Pipeline: List[Dict]

    Pipeline->>ClassParse: process(metadata_list)
    Note right of ClassParse: 按 file_full_path 读取源文件, AST 定位含 test_case_number 的 ClassDef
    ClassParse-->>Pipeline: List[(metadata, class_name, class_node, source_lines)]

    Pipeline->>CorpusParse: process(class_data)
    Note right of CorpusParse: 语句层级遍历方法体, tc.logInfo 作 prompt 分隔符, 控制流块递归提取
    CorpusParse-->>Pipeline: List[(metadata, class_name, List[CodePair])]

    Pipeline->>Enrich: process(corpus_data)
    Note right of Enrich: FIELD_MAPPING 映射输入到输出字段, 填充 TestCaseCorpusItem
    Enrich-->>Pipeline: List[TestCaseCorpusItem]

    Pipeline->>Writer: process(corpus_items)
    Note right of Writer: 以 test_case_number 命名, 每用例一个 JSON 文件
    Writer-->>Pipeline: 输出目录路径

    Pipeline-->>Entry: 完成
    Entry-->>User: 输出目录路径
